      "source": [
        "DAILY VOLUME MATCH"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "GZaNvK3k_SNH"
      }
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "daily_balance = truck_daily.merge(\n",
        "    rehandle_daily,\n",
        "    on=[\"shift_date\", \"dumping_location\", \"material\"],\n",
        "    how=\"left\"\n",
        ")\n",
        "\n",
        "daily_balance[\"recovery_pct\"] = (\n",
        "    daily_balance[\"crusher_tons\"] /\n",
        "    daily_balance[\"pit_tons\"]\n",
        ") * 100\n",
        "\n",
        "daily_balance.head()\n"
